OL,3,C'You saved my life' - abused woman
OL,4,Cmeets police staff she says rescued her
OL,6,FOur correspondent Ann O'Connor reports
OL,7,Fon an emotional reunion
OL,9,FA mother from Rochdale who was raped
OL,10,Fand beaten by her partner over a
OL,11,Fperiod of two years has met the police
OL,12,Fstaff she thanks for saving her life.
OL,14,FHannah Mellor was too scared to talk
OL,15,Fto anyone about the physical and
OL,16,Fsexual abuse Ben Fitton was subjecting
OL,17,Fher to, until he threatened to hurt
OL,18,Fher five year old son.
