OL,3,C'You saved my life' - abused woman
OL,4,Cmeets police staff she says rescued her
OL,6,FSo in June 2023 Hannah knew she had to
OL,7,Fact. She messaged the live chat
OL,8,Fservice on the Greater Manchester
OL,9,FPolice website.
OL,11,FHannah says, 'I could not say the
OL,12,Fwords, they wouldn't come out of my
OL,13,Fmouth. I wanted to say I am going
OL,14,Fthrough serious domestic abuse and I
OL,15,Fdon't know what to do and I don't know
OL,16,Fwhere to turn, so that's why live chat
OL,17,Fwas invaluable to me'.
