OL,3,C'You saved my life' - abused woman
OL,4,Cmeets police staff she says rescued her
OL,6,FEmma says, 'It's hard listening to
OL,7,Fsome of the stories you hear as a call
OL,8,Fhandler. But we're there to help
OL,9,Fpeople and and if I can go home
OL,10,Fknowing I've helped someone then
OL,11,Fthat's fine with me'.
OL,13,FGreater Manchester police has faced
OL,14,Fcriticism in recent years for its
OL,15,Fhandling of domestic abuse cases. The
OL,16,Fforce says live chat is a vital tool
OL,17,Fto tackle cases. There were 85,000
OL,18,Flive chat conversations with Greater
OL,19,FManchester police between August 2024
OL,20,Fand February 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
