OL,3,C'You saved my life' - abused woman
OL,4,Cmeets police staff she says rescued her
OL,6,FThe first officer to see Hannah after
OL,7,Fshe made her complaint, was Detective
OL,8,FSergeant Ruth Thompson. She says "It's
OL,9,Fa very brave decision for people to
OL,10,Fcome forward and we don't
OL,11,Funderestimate that decision. But when
OL,12,Fthey do they will be treated with
OL,13,Frespect and compassion".
OL,15,FThe force is now urging others living
OL,16,Fin abusive relationships to follow
OL,17,FHannah's example and come forward.
